    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT392-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">varaiviṭaik kiḻattiyatu nilaimai tumpikkac colluvāḷāycb
                    ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻi colliyatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered by the confidante, while [he] is behind
                    the hedge, as if talking to a bee about HER state [when awaiting] the time of
                    marriage. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT392">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> amma vāḻiyō vaṇicciṟait tumpi</l>
                    <l> naṉmoḻik kacca millai yavarnāṭ</l>
                    <l> ṭaṇṇa ṉeṭuvaraic cēṟi yāyiṟ</l>
                    <l> kaṭavai miṭainta tuṭavaiyañ ciṟutiṉait</l>
                    <l> tuḷareṟi nuṇṭukaṭ kaḷaiñar taṅkai</l>
                    <l> tamariṟ ṟīrā ḷeṉmō varacar</l>
                    <l> niraicela ṉuṇṭōl pōlap</l>
                    <l> piracan tūṅku malaikiḻa vōrkkē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l> Alas, may you live, bee with adorning wings,</l>
                    <l> fear [to utter] good words is not [necessary]. </l>
                    <l rend="indent"> If you go to the majestic long mountain of his land,</l>
                    <l> say to the master of the mountain, where honeycombs are hanging</l>
                    <l rend="indent2"> like fine shields, going in a row for the king:</l>
                    <l> “she<choice>
                            <seg> won't end </seg>
                            <seg>has not ceased [to live] </seg>
                        </choice>with
                        her people,</l>
                    <l> the younger sister of the pickers in the fine dust,</l>
                    <l rend="indent8"> where they hack weeds </l>
                    <l rend="indent3"> from the little millet by the wood crowded with trespassers.”</l>

                    <lg type="alternate" sameAs="6b">
                        <l>“she has not ceased [to live] with her people”,</l>
                    </lg>
                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
